      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained by a single owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather interior remains supple and fragrant, showing zero signs of wear or creasing on the bolsters. Mechanically, the car is flawless; it comes with a comprehensive, documented service history with every scheduled maintenance performed strictly at the dealership. All electronic systems, from the high-fidelity sound system to the precision navigation, operate as they did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
      "price": 46500.0,
