    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presented is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical health, having undergone a comprehensive high-pressure VANOS overhaul and rod bearing service. This specimen features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and visceral feedback. The chassis is structurally perfect, with a pre-emptively reinforced rear subframe to maintain factory lateral rigidity. The exterior retains its original depth and luster, while the interior leather and switchgear show zero signs of fatigue or UV damage. A mechanically transparent, turnkey machine for the purist collector.",
